The International Conference on Digital Information Processing,

Dubai- UAE
January 28-30, 2015
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
The proposed conference that will be held at Dubai, UAE From January 28-30, 2015 aims to enable researchers build connections between different digital applications.

The conference welcomes papers on the following (but not limited to)research topics:

****Digital Information Processing
****Data Mining
****Wireless Communications
****E-Commerce, E-Marketing, E-Banking

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

The Submission Date is open from now until Jan. 12, 2015
The Last Day for Registration: open from now until Jan. 18, 2015
